org.bamja.core.annotations
Annotation Type BidirectProvidedServices

@Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface BidirectProvidedServices

Collect several provided services of a component, but to deliver this services, the component required a service by the using component.
